Project Description
Silverlight based Mavlink log analyzer. This ise useful for people who wish to examine Mavlink logs. It is developed in C# and Silverlight 4, using a Mavlink library autogenerated in Silverlight 3

Mavlink Packet Viewer is a Silverlight 4 application that is used to examine Mavlink transmission logs that were recorded from applications like QGroundControl and the APM Planner.

This application will be useful to you if you need to examine a Mavlink log at a packet level - for example if you are investigating a crash log, or debugging a new Mavlink implementation etc
